{"tid":2302773,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"本尊正翻！《女神降臨》作者上劉在錫節目　真面目為之驚艷","createTime":"2020-11-27T11:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T11:48:16.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5352b8a52014368ad561f0351839861cf4e39077","tid":2302773,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣漫畫《女神降臨》相當受到歡迎，除了翻拍成真人版韓劇，由一票如同二次元走出來的偶像演出外，漫畫家作者「貓咪（야옹이）」本尊，彷彿是女主角化妝後的真人版也引起話題，包括私生活也廣受到網友關注。近日她登上劉在錫主持節目，本尊竟真的如同修圖一般走出來，讓大家再度覺得不真實。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/27/2906141-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2F2906141-PH.jpg&h=c30a3801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《女神降臨》作者貓咪猶如真人版女主角成熱門話題。（圖／翻攝自meow91__ IG）<br />\n<br />\n貓咪自從公開本尊真面目後，因為超S曲線身材與不科學的臉蛋，引發大票網友注意，然而也因為人紅是非多，她的私生活開始被起底成焦點，先前與老公鬧出醜聞也引發許多爭議，不過與老公離婚後，網友也發現她也展開第二春，與另一漫畫《青春白卷》作者交往中，不時還會放閃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/27/2906168-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2F2906168-PH.jpg&h=547c981b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《女神降臨》作者貓咪現身劉在錫節目。（圖／翻攝自meow91__ IG）<br />\n<br />\n這次為了宣傳即將播出真人版《女神降臨》，貓咪特別登上了劉在錫主持《劉Quiz on the Block》節目。預告播出後不少網友大讚，即便被影片拉寬放大，貓咪本人幾乎與照片一樣，身材和臉蛋都是一線藝人的水準等級。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/27/2906177-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2F2906177-PH.jpg&h=5c2120b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲貓咪本尊節目現身，外貌如同一線女星超級不真實。（圖／翻攝自TvN YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/27/2906179-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2F2906179-PH.jpg&h=0e570bb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《女神降臨》真人版男、女主角同樣不科學。（圖／翻攝自meow91__ IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/27/2906180-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2F2906180-PH.jpg&h=078eaa40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲真人版由車銀優（右起）、文佳煐、黃仁燁主演。（圖／翻攝自meow91__ IG）<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，貓咪還畫出了劉在錫、曹世鎬如果進入漫畫「女神降臨化」會是甚麼模樣，只見劉在錫和曹世鎬在貓咪的畫裡直接「變身成為花美男」，不僅散發出柔焦的光芒，笑容也相當燦爛，不過也因為太於「美化」，讓兩人看到皆忍不住笑了出來，預告一出立刻引發話題。"},{"pid":"a93586045433c6b964c2c69ce2a6640cccb70881","tid":2302773,"uid":261849,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:13:44.000Z","msg":"咁假個樣"},{"pid":"a340781e54b37c3b6d4ca178f2a1b99485aa1030","tid":2302773,"uid":57303,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a93586045433c6b964c2c69ce2a6640cccb70881","tid":2302773,"uid":261849,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:13:44.000Z","msg":"咁假個樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"一睇就知人造人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cee023fccc46144cc9b12c5f71d2361025e635b","tid":2302773,"uid":57490,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:17:34.000Z","msg":"有啲恐怖"},{"pid":"6a21fe5f24aa4e8fabd402c75a9a44b090bd5a00","tid":2302773,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"作者 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇尻死 理撚得佢係呀婆呀"},{"pid":"cb171b8bd5058abeaa88f60a05dfd893ea806acb","tid":2302773,"uid":256952,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:23:42.000Z","msg":"車銀優世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ae292d723ffe05d53260f62ae1fb8e93f98926","tid":2302773,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:24:02.000Z","msg":"男2唔係安孝燮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\"